{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/ada-fitur-baru-di-ciayo-comics/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Ada Fitur Baru di CIAYO Comics","content":"<p>Bro sis sadar ga sih kalau ada yang baru dari CIAYO Comics? Kalau diperhatiin, sudah ada beberapa fitur baru yang menunggu untuk dicoba loh. Yup, ada beberapa fitur baru yang berhasil dikembangkan seiring dengan meningkatnya minat masyarakat yang mengunjungi CIAYO Comics Situs Komik Online Gratis. Mau tau apa aja?</p>\n<h3><strong>1. Fitur Bahasa</strong></h3>\n<div id=\"attachment_18903\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-18903\" data-attachment-id=\"18903\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/ada-fitur-baru-di-ciayo-comics/attachment/isi-ada-fitur-baru-608-x-320-6/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/isi-ada-fitur-baru-608-x-320-6.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Piihan Bahasa (CIAYO Comics)\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/isi-ada-fitur-baru-608-x-320-6.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/isi-ada-fitur-baru-608-x-320-6.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-18903\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/isi-ada-fitur-baru-608-x-320-6.jpg\" alt=\"Piihan Bahasa (CIAYO Comics)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-18903\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Piihan Bahasa (CIAYO Comics)</p></div>\n<p>Meskipun CIAYO Comics merupakan platform buatan anak negeri, tetapi kenyamanan para pembaca setia menjadi yang utama. Belum setahun hadir sebagai platform komik Indonesia, CIAYO Comics memberi bro sis pilihan bahasa, yaitu bahasa Inggris. Jadi gak ada lagi deh “Males ah, bacanya. Monoton”. Eits, ini juga bisa jadi ajang belajar bahasa buat bro sis loh hehe.</p>\n<p>Selain pembaca lokal, CIAYO Comics juga sudah mulai dibaca oleh para pecinta komik dari mancanegara. Jadi fitur bahasa Inggris ini pun menjadi oase bagi pecinta komik yang tidak mengerti bahasa Indonesia, tetapi tertarik dengan art dan cerita-cerita karya kreator lokal.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_18906\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-18906\" data-attachment-id=\"18906\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/ada-fitur-baru-di-ciayo-comics/attachment/isi-ada-fitur-baru-608-x-320-5/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/isi-ada-fitur-baru-608-x-320-5.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"(CIAYO Comics)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;(CIAYO Comics)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/isi-ada-fitur-baru-608-x-320-5.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/isi-ada-fitur-baru-608-x-320-5.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-18906\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/isi-ada-fitur-baru-608-x-320-5.jpg\" alt=\"(CIAYO Comics)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-18906\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">(CIAYO Comics)</p></div>\n<p>Buat yang mau langsung coba, caranya gampang. Update dulu aplikasinya. Klik pilihan <strong>more</strong>, lalu s<strong>etting – comic language</strong>. Pilih deh bahasa yang bro sis mau. Jangan lupa simpan ya. Bro sis langsung nikmatin deh.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_18909\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-18909\" data-attachment-id=\"18909\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/ada-fitur-baru-di-ciayo-comics/attachment/isi-ada-fitur-baru-608-x-320-4/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/isi-ada-fitur-baru-608-x-320-4.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Pilihan Bahasa yang Muncul Saat Membuka Aplikasi (CIAYO Comics)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Pilihan Bahasa yang Muncul Saat Membuka Aplikasi (CIAYO Comics)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/isi-ada-fitur-baru-608-x-320-4.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/isi-ada-fitur-baru-608-x-320-4.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-18909\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/isi-ada-fitur-baru-608-x-320-4.jpg\" alt=\"Pilihan Bahasa yang Muncul Saat Membuka Aplikasi (CIAYO Comics)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-18909\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Pilihan bahasa yang muncul saat membuka aplikasi (CIAYO Comics)</p></div>\n<p>Oh iya, buat yang masih bingung, tenang aja. Soalnya kalau sudah <em>update</em> biasanya pas buka aplikasinya langsung muncul deh pilihan bahasanya.</p>\n<h3><strong>2. Fitur <em>Search</em></strong></h3>\n<div id=\"attachment_18918\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-18918\" data-attachment-id=\"18918\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/ada-fitur-baru-di-ciayo-comics/attachment/isi-ada-fitur-baru-608-x-320-1/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/isi-ada-fitur-baru-608-x-320-1.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"(CIAYO Comics)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;(CIAYO Comics)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/isi-ada-fitur-baru-608-x-320-1.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/isi-ada-fitur-baru-608-x-320-1.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-18918\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/isi-ada-fitur-baru-608-x-320-1.jpg\" alt=\"(CIAYO Comics)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-18918\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">(CIAYO Comics)</p></div>\n<p>Buat bro sis yang dari kemarinan udah cape – cape nge-<em>scroll</em> sampai bawah buat cari komik favorit, CIAYO Comics memberi hadiah atas apresiasi kalian dengan menambahkan fitur <strong><em>search</em></strong>. Fitur ini gak cuma memudahkan mencari judul komik, loh. Tapi juga mencari genre dan nama <em>author</em>.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_18915\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-18915\" data-attachment-id=\"18915\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/ada-fitur-baru-di-ciayo-comics/attachment/isi-ada-fitur-baru-608-x-320-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/isi-ada-fitur-baru-608-x-320-2.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Fitur search (CIAYO Comics)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Fitur search (CIAYO Comics)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/isi-ada-fitur-baru-608-x-320-2.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/isi-ada-fitur-baru-608-x-320-2.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-18915\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/isi-ada-fitur-baru-608-x-320-2.jpg\" alt=\"Fitur search (CIAYO Comics)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-18915\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Fitur search (CIAYO Comics)</p></div>\n<p>Kamu bisa mengetikkan judul komik, genre dan nama author. Oh iya sedikit <em>tips &amp; trick</em>, kalau bro sis mau mencari genre, langsung aja ketik genrenya. Gak usah menggunakan kata komik. Misalnya “r<em>omance</em>” atau “c<em>omedy</em>”.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_18912\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-18912\" data-attachment-id=\"18912\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/ada-fitur-baru-di-ciayo-comics/attachment/isi-ada-fitur-baru-608-x-320-3/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/isi-ada-fitur-baru-608-x-320-3.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"(CIAYO Comics)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;(CIAYO Comics)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/isi-ada-fitur-baru-608-x-320-3.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/isi-ada-fitur-baru-608-x-320-3.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-18912\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/isi-ada-fitur-baru-608-x-320-3.jpg\" alt=\"(CIAYO Comics)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-18912\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">(CIAYO Comics)</p></div>\n<p>Gimana? Makin mudah kan. Langsung aja deh <em>update</em> aplikasi yang ada di <em>handphone</em> kalian. Psst, buat yang belum punya, langsung <em>download</em> aplikasinya dan nikmati kemudahan membaca komik favorit kalian.</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"c4a54a50-967e-58ca-b9dc-613333e437b4"}}}